# ğŸ› ï¸ How to Run the Project Locally

## **1. Clone the repository**
```sh
git clone https://github.com/navyasharon/fitscore-ai.git
cd fitscore-ai
2. Backend Setup (Deno)
Go to backend folder:
cd backend
------Create .env:
       ANTHROPIC_API_KEY=your_key_here
Run backend:
  deno task dev

Backend runs at:
     http://localhost:8000

3. Frontend Setup (React)
Navigate to frontend:
cd ../frontend
     npm install
     npm run dev
Frontend runs at:

    http://localhost:5173

ğŸ“Œ How to Use

