âŒ Why Backend Cannot Be Deployed (Yet)

Zypher writes internal metadata to:

.zypher/


Cloud hosts like Deno Deploy / Netlify Functions / Vercel Edge are read-only, so they block the agent runtime.

Local backend is required.
     

